(30, 1, '2013-07-15 14:01:17', '2013-07-15 14:01:17', '&nbsp;\n<h3 dir="ltr"><span style="color: #339966;">Hi all!</span></h3>\n<h4 dir="ltr">My name is Andre and I am one of the founders of The Startup Scholarship. It''s been an incredible journey so far, but it''s only starting now. We have an incredible first graduate class of 25 students from 9 different countries. These are 25 outstanding young business leaders looking to disrupt their own lives and seeking an out-of-the-box experience. This is the place we are launching for you guys to get to know more about them.</h4>\n<h4 dir="ltr">We hope you consider their will to join this initiative as a motivation strength for your application in the future. We wish to disrupt how summer experiences are built, to make each day an inspirational number of hours that will contribute for your choice of starting up.</h4>\n<h4 dir="ltr">Come and check the posts, perfectly assembed and curated by Michal Gaszynski about our participants, startups and organizations involved with this program.</h4>\n<h4 dir="ltr">Best wishes and we hope to see your name in application processes in the future,</h4>\n<h4 dir="ltr">André Albuquerque and The Startup Scholarship team</h4>\n<h3 dir="ltr"><span style="color: #18951d;"><strong> </strong></span></h3>\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;', 'Welcome!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '26-autosave', '', '', '2013-07-15 14:01:17', '2013-07-15 14:01:17', '', 26, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/26-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(402, 1, '2013-09-03 16:24:03', '2013-09-03 16:24:03', '<a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Michal.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-399" alt="Michal" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Michal.png" /></a> <a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Whistle_a1.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-127" alt="Whistle_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Whistle_a1.png" /></a>\n<h3>Michal "Ain''t No Mountain High Enough" Malcek</h3>\n26. Rimavska Sobota, Slovakia.\n<h3 dir="ltr">INTERNSHIP:</h3>\nBusiness intern at Whistle. Doing initial marketing strategy, story and creating basic press releases from the marketing point of view.\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE PAST:</h3>\nMichal studied CEMS in Prague and Budapest. He did two internships at Google, in Prague and Dublin. He is also the co-founder of a local online retailer selling branded clothes in his town (<a href="http://www.activestyle.sk">www.activestyle.sk</a>).\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE FUTURE:</h3>\nCurrently Michal will try to start a simple, local freelancer-like platform focused only on marketing tasks. He would like to use his experience and contacts gained during The Startup Scholarship program and share them on local startup events, present the Lisbon startup experience, teach his local guys about lean startup methodology and growth hacking. He wants to stay in Slovakia for now and start his business. Hopefully in the future he will gain more international startup experience.\n<h3>CREATIVITY INSPIRATION:</h3>\n<div>"By doing a creative direct marketing campaign for Google AdWords with a new, much better targeted approach (reaching the right segment with the right, suitable example) we reached extraordinary level of efficiency that was not seen before in such channel."</div>\n<h3 dir="ltr">WOULD INVEST 1 MILLION $ IN:</h3>\n"I would target one of the biggest problems of young people in Europe and USA - unemployment &amp; unemployability. I would build a platform connecting as many universities, students and companies as possible, to help companies get done stuff cheaper and review a student before hiring. For students it would give relevant practical experience with little effort to find an opportunity."\n<h3><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 27px; font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif;">FAVORITE PLACE ON EARTH:</span></h3>\n<p dir="ltr">His grandpa''s house, because it is so calm and close to the nature.</p>', 'Startup Scholar: Michal', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '398-revision-3', '', '', '2013-09-03 16:24:03', '2013-09-03 16:24:03', '', 398, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/398-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
