(32, 1, '2013-07-14 23:54:33', '2013-07-14 23:54:33', '&nbsp;\r\n<p dir="ltr"><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/TiagoRamos.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-27 alignnone" alt="TiagoRamos" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/TiagoRamos.png" width="250" height="250" /></a><img class="size-large wp-image-28 alignnone" style="font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; line-height: 19px;" alt="Whistle_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Whistle_a.png" width="250" height="250" /></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>TIAGO "BE YOURSELF" RAMOS</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">22. LISBON, PORTUGAL.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>INTERNSHIP:</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">CONTENT AND SOCIAL MEDIA POSTS CREATION AT WHISTLE.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>IN THE PAST:</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">CYCLED 1500 KM IN 1 YEAR. PASSED DRIVING LICENSE EXAM WITH 40 DEGREES OF FEVER. USED TO MAKE 20 SIMPLE CALCULATIONS IN 17 SECONDS.</p>\r\n<strong>IN THE FUTURE:</strong>\r\n<p dir="ltr">WANTS TO FINISH HIS COURSE, MARRY HIS GIRLFRIEND AND START A FAMILY. WILL WORK HARD FOR HIS BLOG www.theopinion.pt.to. WOULD LIKE TO LIVE IN SWEDEN.</p>\r\n<strong>CREATIVITY INSPIRATION:</strong>\r\n<p dir="ltr">"SNATCH"-ALL THE ROLES ARE PERFECTLY LINKED. A VERY FUNNY AND UNREALISTIC STORY.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>WOULD INVEST 1 MILLION $ IN:</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">"SMART HOUSE" SYSTEM. ALL CONTROLLED FROM YOUR SMARTPHONE: DOORS, WINDOWS, KITCHEN, MACHINES, SOUND SYSTEM AND TV. PLUS A CAR!</p>\r\n<strong>FAVORITE PLACE ON EARTH:</strong>\r\n<p dir="ltr">BALAIA GOLF VILLAGE. ALGARVE, PORTUGAL.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'j', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '26-revision-3', '', '', '2013-07-14 23:54:33', '2013-07-14 23:54:33', '', 26, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/26-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
