(66, 1, '2013-07-15 14:01:28', '2013-07-15 14:01:28', '&nbsp;\r\n<h3 dir="ltr"><span style="color: #339966;">Hi all!</span></h3>\r\n<h4 dir="ltr">My name is Andre and I am one of the founders of The Startup Scholarship. It''s been an incredible journey so far, but it''s only starting now. We have an incredible first graduate class of 25 students from 9 different countries. These are 25 outstanding young business leaders looking to disrupt their own lives and seeking an out-of-the-box experience. This is the place we are launching for you guys to get to know more about them.</h4>\r\n<h4 dir="ltr">We hope you consider their will to join this initiative as a motivation strength for your application in the future. We wish to disrupt how summer experiences are built, to make each day an inspirational number of hours that will contribute for your choice of starting up.</h4>\r\n<h4 dir="ltr">Come and check the posts, perfectly assembed and curated by Michal Gaszynski about our participants, startups and organizations involved with this program.</h4>\r\n<h4 dir="ltr">Best wishes and we hope to see your name in application processes in the future,</h4>\r\n<h4 dir="ltr">André Albuquerque and The Startup Scholarship team</h4>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr"><span style="color: #18951d;"><strong> </strong></span></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Welcome!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '26-revision-9', '', '', '2013-07-15 14:01:28', '2013-07-15 14:01:28', '', 26, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/26-revision-9/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(68, 1, '2013-07-16 21:11:36', '2013-07-16 21:11:36', '<h3><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/WeGoOut_a-1.png"><img class=" wp-image-126 alignleft" alt="WeGoOut_a (1)" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/WeGoOut_a-1.png" width="137" height="137" /></a>WE GO OUT</h3>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #808080;">EST. JULY 2012</span></h3>\r\n<h3>INDUSTRY: ENTERTAINMENT/SOCIAL PLATFORM</h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">WHAT?</h3>\r\nIT GUIDES YOU TO THE BEST WAYS TO SPEND FREE TIME IN YOUR CITY.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">HOW?</h3>\r\nBY RECOMMENDING THE MOST INTERESTING AND POPULAR EVENTS AROUND YOU. "WE GO OUT" POSTS PHOTOS FROM EVERYWHERE THERE IS SOMETHING COOL GOING ON, PROVIDES SUGGESTIONS BASING ON YOUR FRIENDS PREFERENCES, LETS YOU CONNECT, MAKE PLANS TOGETHER AND RATE EVERYTHING YOU EXPERIENCED.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">ORIGIN OF THE IDEA:</h3>\r\nIN THE BEGINNING WE WANTED TO HELP PEOPLE TO MEET EACH OTHER AT NIGHT PARTIES. LATER THE IDEA EVOLVED TO SOMETHING BETTER AND MORE POWERFUL: "WHERE ARE THE BEST PARTIES TONIGHT?". IT IS HARD TO FIND THE RIGHT PLACE TO GO OUT WHEN YOU ARE IN A NEW OR A BIG CITY BUT "WE GO OUT" WILL HELP YOU TO!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Startup: We Go Out', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'startup-we-go-out', '', '', '2013-07-17 13:53:04', '2013-07-17 13:53:04', '', 0, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/?p=68', 0, 'post', '', 0),
