(400, 1, '2013-09-02 15:30:23', '2013-09-02 15:30:23', '<a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Michal.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-399" alt="Michal" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Michal.png" /></a> <a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Whistle_a1.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-127" alt="Whistle_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Whistle_a1.png" /></a>\n<h3>Michal "Ain''t N Mountain High Enough" Malcek</h3>\n. Rimavska Sobota, Slovakia.\n<h3 dir="ltr">INTERNSHIP:</h3>\nMarket research for UmamiBox.\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE PAST:</h3>\n"High school in the States was a great experience. Pairing engineering studies and management helped to gain insight into both worlds. My first 3DS made me realize how little I knew."\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE FUTURE:</h3>\n"I can''t wait to graduate. I can''t wait to go back to Madrid and start starting things. I can''t wait to travel again."\n<h3>CREATIVITY INSPIRATION:</h3>\n<div>The photographer making pictures with mirrors. Showing both the picture and whats in front of it.</div>\n<h3 dir="ltr">WOULD INVEST 1 MILLION $ IN:</h3>\nThis crowdsource idea helping to lower the cost and barrier of entry for books in schools.\n<h3 dir="ltr">FAVORITE PLACE ON EARTH:</h3>\n<p dir="ltr">Hasn''t found it yet.</p>', 'Startup Scholar: Michal', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '398-revision', '', '', '2013-09-02 15:30:23', '2013-09-02 15:30:23', '', 398, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/398-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
