(116, 1, '2013-07-18 20:09:58', '2013-07-18 20:09:58', '<h3 dir="ltr"><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/ConsultaClick_a.png"><img class=" wp-image-117 alignleft" alt="ConsultaClick_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/ConsultaClick_a.png" width="137" height="137" /></a>ConsultaClick</h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr"><span style="color: #808080;">EST. JULY 2011</span></h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">INDUSTRY: MEDICAL SERVICE</h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">WHAT?</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">ConsultaClick is changing the method of scheduling appointments with health care professionals.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">HOW?</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Easy to use platform recommends you the right medical service fit to the problem you are facing. The service categorizes professionals, matches your suitable location, current availability and presents ratings and opinions. Finally, ConsultaClick lets you contact and schedule an appointment.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">ORIGIN OF THE IDEA:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">The idea of ConsultaClick began in 2010 after the founder had an accident. After that he constantly had to book or reschedule his orthopedic and physiotherapy sessions. With this need he realized that there is no efficient services allowing to get more info about the doctor or to book online health appointments. So if we can book online a flight, a hotel, or a restaurant why can’t we book a health appointment? This is how ConsultaClick.com was born.</p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Startup: ConsultaClick', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'startup-consultaclick', '', '', '2013-07-18 20:09:58', '2013-07-18 20:09:58', '', 0, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/?p=116', 0, 'post', '', 0),
