(379, 1, '2013-08-21 11:54:18', '2013-08-21 11:54:18', '<h3>Stig "I''m on a boat" Dreyer</h3>\n23. Schwanewede, Germany.\n<h3 dir="ltr">INTERNSHIP:</h3>\nCrowdProcess - "Testing the CrowdProcess API while developing and porting awesome embarrassingly parallel problems for/to the platform".\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE PAST:</h3>\nDespite being born in Germany and spending most of his time there there, he does not consider himself German. Stig spent a big part of his childhood in Spain, lived for 2 years in New Zealand, studied in the Netherlands, lived for a bit in Shanghai and is just about to start a journey around the world. The best thing to happen for him was to setup his own company 5 years ago.\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE FUTURE:</h3>\nStig loves traveling but does not like to stay long in one place. This is why he plans to combine his passion with a well paying job. Next year Stig will either do his master in business strategy or start working for a multinational.\n<h3>CREATIVITY INSPIRATION:</h3>\n<div>"Even though I don''t have a particular example I believe that creativity flourishes when people try to solve a particular problem that is bugging them. In doing this they gain happiness".</div>\n<h3 dir="ltr">WOULD INVEST 1 MILLION $ IN:</h3>\n"Even though I don''t have a particular idea right now I''d imagine it to have a great deal to do with technology. Or maybe something completely different. I have the opinion that there are so many things that are unexplored yet".\n<h3 dir="ltr">FAVORITE PLACE ON EARTH:</h3>\n<p dir="ltr">New Zealand.</p>', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '377-revision', '', '', '2013-08-21 11:54:18', '2013-08-21 11:54:18', '', 377, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/377-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
