(176, 1, '2013-07-20 20:29:09', '2013-07-20 20:29:09', '<h3><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/CrowdProcess_a.png"><img class=" wp-image-118 alignleft" alt="CrowdProcess_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/CrowdProcess_a.png" width="137" height="137" /></a>CrowdProcess</h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr"><span style="color: #808080;">EST: NOVEMBER 2012</span></h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">INDUSTRY: DIGITAL SERVICES</h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">WHAT?</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">"We''re turning the internet into a SUPERCOMPUTER"</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">HOW?</h3>\r\nWhile browsing the web, people waste a lot of processing power on their computers. CrowdProcess enables websites to collect tiny amounts of that wasted processing power and turn it into a SINGLE SUPERCOMPUTER that can be used by everyone.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">THE ORIGIN OF THE IDEA:</h3>\r\n"Our CTO had a huge matrix to process and had no money to buy the infrastructure necessary to do it on Amazon''s AWS. So he started thinking about ways to process that matrix using the processing power of website viewers... so that''s how CrowdProcess was born!"', 'Startup: CrowdProcess', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'startup-crowdprocess-2', '', '', '2013-07-20 20:32:00', '2013-07-20 20:32:00', '', 0, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/?p=176', 0, 'post', '', 0),
