(385, 1, '2013-08-26 18:27:30', '2013-08-26 18:27:30', '<a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/BorjaLars.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-386" alt="BorjaLars" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/BorjaLars.png" /></a> <a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/UmamiBox_a.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-125" alt="UmamiBox_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/UmamiBox_a.png" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Borja "Back &amp; Forth" de las Ilanderas</h3>\r\n24. Madrid, Spain.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">INTERNSHIP:</h3>\r\nMarket research for UmamiBox.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE PAST:</h3>\r\n"High school in the States was a great experience. Pairing engineering studies and management helped to gain insight into both worlds. My first 3DS made me realize how little I knew."\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE FUTURE:</h3>\r\n"I can''t wait to graduate. I can''t wait to go back to Madrid and start starting things. I can''t wait to travel again."\r\n<h3>CREATIVITY INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n<div>The photographer making pictures with mirrors. Showing both the picture and whats in front of it.</div>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">WOULD INVEST 1 MILLION $ IN:</h3>\r\nThis crowdsource idea helping to lower the cost and barrier of entry for books in schools.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">FAVORITE PLACE ON EARTH:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Hasn''t found it yet.</p>', 'Startup Scholar: Borja', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'startup-scholar-borja', '', '', '2013-08-26 18:27:30', '2013-08-26 18:27:30', '', 0, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/?p=385', 0, 'post', '', 0),
