(185, 1, '2013-07-19 13:18:02', '2013-07-19 13:18:02', '<h3><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/JoaoCavaco.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-147" alt="JoaoCavaco" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/JoaoCavaco.png" /></a> <a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Origama_a.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-121" alt="Origama_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Origama_a.png" /></a></h3>\r\n<h3>João "Around The World" Cavaco</h3>\r\n21. Lisbon, Portugal.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">INTERNSHIP:</h3>\r\nDeveloping the upcoming app for Origama.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE PAST:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Practiced several theatre plays for a year but never got to perform in public (chaotic theatre). Learned many of his life lessons while riding a bike. Trained judo for a very long time.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE FUTURE:</h3>\r\nJoão would like to go on traveling. Wants to work in all sorts of different settings and to make something on his own.\r\n<h3>CREATIVITY INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">The invention of bread. Some primitive man or woman decided to turn cereal into white powder, and that into food that no longer resembles the ingredients in shape or color. How did that happen? Genius.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">WOULD INVEST 1 MILLION $ IN:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">A teaching website, with videos about all sorts of subjects that viewers could view as fast or as slowly as they want. It goes like this. Film a very detailed version of a well structured class. Divide it into lots of different parts (such as subchapters in a book). Then sum it up in a shorter version and film that one too, also dividing it into parts. Keep filming different versions, and don’t lose sense of structure. Then build a website in which viewers can select the level of detail they want for their videos, and adjust the detail level throughout the class by jumping between versions in the end of each part. The same principle could allow viewers to push “explain it in other words” or “give me an example” buttons.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">FAVORITE PLACE ON EARTH:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">The middle of the ocean, with no land in sight.</p>', 'Startup Scholar: Joao', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '146-revision-9', '', '', '2013-07-19 13:18:02', '2013-07-19 13:18:02', '', 146, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/146-revision-9/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
