(296, 1, '2013-07-29 23:13:30', '2013-07-29 23:13:30', '<h3><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/RafaelCosta.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-294" alt="RafaelCosta" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/RafaelCosta.png" /></a> <a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Emove_a.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-119" alt="Emove_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Emove_a.png" /></a></h3>\r\n<h3>Rafael "I''m Sexy &amp; I Know It" Costa</h3>\r\n23. Lisbon, Portugal.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">INTERNSHIP:</h3>\r\nInformation computations for EMOVE.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE PAST:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Rafael studied electrical engineering. He had the time of his life in Louvain-la-Neuve. It is his 1st entrepreneurial experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE FUTURE:</h3>\r\nHe is not sure yet. First needs to finish his thesis. He hopes to have a better idea of how a startups work. He would like to live somewhere cool in Europe.\r\n\r\n<span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 27px; font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif;">CREATIVITY INSPIRATION:</span>\r\n<p dir="ltr">"Honda Hands" advertising.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">WOULD INVEST 1 MILLION $ IN:</h3>\r\nHe has so many ideas that it''s hard to decide, but for sure it would be something where he could talk to people.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">FAVORITE PLACE ON EARTH:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Earth.</p>', 'Startup Scholar: Rafael', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '293-revision-2', '', '', '2013-07-29 23:13:30', '2013-07-29 23:13:30', '', 293, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/293-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
