 style="text-align: justify;">practical approach, pushing you to think outside the box. Pirates stimulate creativity, provide</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">business tools to develop participants'' ideas and enable to pitch them in front of <span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;">the professional </span><span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;">jury.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;"> "This week is all about teamwork, critic thought, learning, creativity and </span><span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px;">out-of-the-box thinking".</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;"></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">Startup Pirates invited some participants from previous edition of the event who shared their</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">lessons learnt from best projects expanded during the program. They talked about how much</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">they got support in the development of their concepts and how they evolved from entrepreneurs</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">protective of their business ideas to ones always sharing, discussing and open for the criticism.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">Startup Scholars could discuss specific business ideas and models and ask questions regarding</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">any entrepreneurial issues. In the end the Startup Pirates founders admitted how is it to struggle</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;">with getting financed and developing a sustainable revenue model for the program like this.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"></p>\r\n<a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/935041_523425791058710_504029171_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-204" alt="935041_523425791058710_504029171_n" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/935041_523425791058710_504029171_n.jpg" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Community immersion: Startup Pirates', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '196-revision-32', '', '', '2013-07-22 18:26:27', '2013-07-22 18:26:27', '', 196, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/196-revision-32/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
