(265, 1, '2013-07-25 18:01:42', '2013-07-25 18:01:42', '<h3><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Mobitto_a.png"><img class=" wp-image-120 alignleft" alt="Mobitto_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Mobitto_a.png" width="137" height="137" /></a>Mobitto</h3>\n<h3 dir="ltr">EST: Mobitto was established in June 2011 as a UK based company. Approximately 1 year afterwards, it received an investment and moved its headquarters to Lisbon.</h3>\n<h3 dir="ltr">INDUSTRY: DIGITAL SERVICES</h3>\n<h3 dir="ltr">WHAT?</h3>\n<p dir="ltr">"We''re turning the internet into a SUPERCOMPUTER"</p>\n\n<h3 dir="ltr">HOW?</h3>\nWhile browsing the web, people waste a lot of processing power on their computers. CrowdProcess enables websites to collect tiny amounts of that wasted processing power and turn it into a SINGLE SUPERCOMPUTER that can be used by everyone.\n<h3 dir="ltr">THE ORIGIN OF THE IDEA:</h3>\n"Our CTO had a huge matrix to process and had no money to buy the infrastructure necessary to do it on Amazon''s AWS. So he started thinking about ways to process that matrix using the processing power of website viewers... so that''s how CrowdProcess was born!"', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '250-revision-15', '', '', '2013-07-25 18:01:42', '2013-07-25 18:01:42', '', 250, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/250-revision-15/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(271, 1, '2013-07-25 19:39:39', '2013-07-25 19:39:39', '<h3><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Mobitto_a.png"><img class=" wp-image-120 alignleft" alt="Mobitto_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Mobitto_a.png" width="137" height="137" /></a>Mobitto</h3>\n<h3 dir="ltr"><span style="color: #808080;">EST: June 2011 in UK. 1 year later moved to Lisbon.</span></h3>\n<h3 dir="ltr">INDUSTRY: LOYALTY PROGRAM</h3>\n<h3 dir="ltr">WHAT?</h3>\n<p dir="ltr">Lets users earn points and rewards at their favorite places.</p>\n\n<h3 dir="ltr">HOW?</h3>\nMobitto makes loyalty program a game where you can build your own network with friends. It recognizes the places that you may like and proposes the ones that are around you. You earn points for using and sharing experience from specific products services, that later can be exchanged for rewards.\n<h3 dir="ltr">THE ORIGIN OF THE IDEA:</h3>\nMobitto was born as a PhD thesis of one of the co-founders, with a clear goal: "Improve the way people interact with their favorite brand and the other way around". In the beginning it was basing on the discount approach but later it shifted towards loyalty &amp; gamification. This was the result of many talks and meetings with (potential) clients, users and team members. The Mobitto team wants to leverage the most powerful marketing tool any marketeer can have: Word of Mouth. They just adapted it to the way people communicate and interact nowadays-through social networks and mobile phones.', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '250-revision-21', '', '', '2013-07-25 19:39:39', '2013-07-25 19:39:39', '', 250, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/250-revision-21/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(268, 1, '2013-07-25 19:32:26', '2013-07-25 19:32:26', '<h3><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Mobitto_a.png"><img class=" wp-image-120 alignleft" alt="Mobitto_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Mobitto_a.png" width="137" height="137" /></a>Mobitto</h3>\n<h3 dir="ltr"><span style="color: #808080;">EST: June 2011 in UK. 1 year later moved to Lisbon.</span></h3>\n<h3 dir="ltr">INDUSTRY: LOYALTY PROGRAM</h3>\n<h3 dir="ltr">WHAT?</h3>\n<p dir="ltr">Lets users earn points and rewards at their favorite places.</p>\n<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 27px; font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif;">HOW?</span></p>\nMobitto makes loyalty program a game where you can build your own networks with friends. It recognizes the places that you may like and proposes the ones that are around you. You earn points for using and sharing experience from specific products services, that later can be exchanged for rewards.\n<h3 dir="ltr">THE ORIGIN OF THE IDEA:</h3>\nMobitto was born as a PhD thesis of one of the co-founders, with a clear goal: "Improve the way people interact with their favorite brand and the other way around". In the beginning it was basing on the discount approach but later it shifted towards loyalty &amp; gamification. This was the result of many talks and meetings with (potential) clients, users and team members. We want to leverage the most powerful marketing tool any marketeer can have: Word of Mouth. We just adapted it to the way people communicate and interact nowadays, through social networks and mobile phones.\n\nHaving that said, we didn''t forget the consumers. Nowadays we present ourselves has a universal loyalty app that rewards people for consuming, sharing and recommending the things they like the most. Ever thought you could get paid just for giving your opinion to a friends? Well, now you can...', 'Startup: Mobitto', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '250-revision-18', '', '', '2013-07-25 19:32:26', '2013-07-25 19:32:26', '', 250, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/250-revision-18/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(266, 1, '2013-07-25 18:13:36', '2013-07-25 18:13:36', '<h3><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Mobitto_a.png"><img class=" wp-image-120 alignleft" alt="Mobitto_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Mobitto_a.png" width="137" height="137" /></a>Mobitto</h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">EST: Mobitto was established in June 2011 as a UK based company. Approximately 1 year afterwards, it received an investment and moved its headquarters to Lisbon.</h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">INDUSTRY:</h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">WHAT?</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Lets users earn points and rewards at their favorite places.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 27px; font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif;">HOW?</span></p>\r\nMobitto recognizes the places that you may like and proposes the ones that are around you. For using and sharing experience from specific products services you earn points that later can be\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">THE ORIGIN OF THE IDEA:</h3>\r\nOriginally, Mobitto is born as a spin-off of José Simões (CEO &amp; co-founder) PhD thesis, which had a clear goal: "Improve the way people interact with their favourite brand and the other way around". We started with the discount approach but soon realised that was a dead end. Therefore, about 1 year ago we shifted towards a loyalty + gamification approach, which is a common pain every business to take care of.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThis was the result several of talks and meetings with many (potential) clients, users and team members. We want to leverage the most powerful marketing tool any marketeer can have: Word of Mouth. We just adapted it to the way people communicate and interact nowadays, through social networks and mobile phones.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHaving that said, we didn''t forget the consumers. Nowadays we present ourselves has a universal loyalty app that rewards people for consuming, sharing and recommending the