(297, 1, '2013-07-30 19:07:04', '2013-07-30 19:07:04', '<h3><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/AlvaroGarcia.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-298 alignleft" alt="AlvaroGarcia" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/AlvaroGarcia.png" width="250" height="250" /></a> <a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/TableAndFriends_a.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-124 alignnone" alt="TableAndFriends_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/TableAndFriends_a.png" width="250" height="250" /></a></h3>\r\n<h3>Álvaro "Precious" Recuero</h3>\r\n29. The small town in the famous region of "La Mancha" near Toledo, Spain. Hot as hell in summer, and freezing cold in winter too at times.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">INTERNSHIP:</h3>\r\n"I am with Table And Friends. I have taken the role of DevOps in the startup for overseeing the main operations of the startup helping them with as much knowledge I can bring with me to the ¨Table¨ actually".\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE PAST:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Lived in Dublin, Stockholm, Lisbon and Madrid to name a few. Studied Distributed Systems during several years and will shortly complete a Master Degree in that too. Most importantly, learnt to grow professionally and personally while making others grow at the same time.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE FUTURE:</h3>\r\n"I only have one dream, travel the world while working in what I love the most." If possible, making it my own and serving to a sustainable purpose useful for the rest of human beings in the planet.\r\n<h3>CREATIVITY INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">AirBnB. It is a very good and inspiring story of that anyone interested in building their own company can map their dream to reality at a startup. That is why Álvaro believes in the idea of T&amp;F and even though there are many things yet to be polished on their site, keeping it simple and very related to social interactions is so far a major achievement they already have in place for the future of the company.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">WOULD INVEST 1 MILLION $ IN:</h3>\r\nSomething related to cuisine, traveling and people, or who knows ... a mix of a few of them.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">FAVORITE PLACE ON EARTH:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">California or anywhere else near a coastline and a good set of waves.</p>', 'Startup Scholar: Alvaro', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'startup-scholar-alvaro', '', '', '2013-07-30 19:07:04', '2013-07-30 19:07:04', '', 0, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/?p=297', 0, 'post', '', 0),
