(308, 1, '2013-08-03 20:41:49', '2013-08-03 20:41:49', '<h3><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/IslamMustafa.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-309" alt="IslamMustafa" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/IslamMustafa.png" /></a> <a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/TableAndFriends_a.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-124" alt="TableAndFriends_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/TableAndFriends_a.png" /></a></h3>\r\n<h3>Islam "This Is How We Do It" Mustafa</h3>\r\n24. Nasr City, Egypt.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">INTERNSHIP:</h3>\r\nWorks with Table &amp; Friends and develops their new internal and external APIs (the way other application developers can talk to T&amp;F), and builds the foundation of their new mobile application.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE PAST:</h3>\r\nIslam has started his own startup in Egypt more than a year ago with his friends. It is called "Integreight". They are making a new device that will change the way engineering students learn electronics. The team already got a US patent to protect the idea, made a prototype and raised the first round of funds.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE FUTURE:</h3>\r\nHe would like to sell his company for 1 billion USD!\r\n<h3>CREATIVITY INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">"One of the best geeky startups I really like right now and consider them very creative is CrowdProcess. I was thinking of the same idea 2 years ago and didn''t expect to find that the only company in world working on it would be in the same building as I am. For those who don''t know CrowdProcess, they want to take advantage of the millions of websites visitors world wide and connect them all to build the largest super duper computer that can solve huge computational problems much faster than the normal super computers and even cheaper."</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">WOULD INVEST 1 MILLION $ IN:</h3>\r\nOf course he would inject it in his startup-Integreight. That way, they could launch their second product (which is patent-able as well) much faster. "Because you know, life is much easier with cash".\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">FAVORITE PLACE ON EARTH:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Any place with a computer terminal and Internet connection!</p>', 'Startup Scholar: Islam', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'startup-scholar-islam', '', '', '2013-08-03 22:33:48', '2013-08-03 22:33:48', '', 0, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/?p=308', 0, 'post', '', 2),
