ould launch their second product (which is patent-able as well) much faster. "Because you know, life is much easier with cash".\n<h3 dir="ltr">FAVORITE PLACE ON EARTH:</h3>\n<p dir="ltr">Any place with a computer terminal and Internet connection!</p>', 'Startup Scholar: Islam', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '308-autosave', '', '', '2013-08-05 17:30:02', '2013-08-05 17:30:02', '', 308, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/308-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(343, 1, '2013-08-09 20:15:28', '2013-08-09 20:15:28', '<h3><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/BrunoCoelho.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-344" alt="BrunoCoelho" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/BrunoCoelho.png" /></a> <a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Seeders_a1.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-345" alt="Seeders_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Seeders_a1.png" /></a></h3>\r\n<h3>Bruno "Supertramp" Coelho</h3>\r\n23. Lisbon, Portugal.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">INTERNSHIP:</h3>\r\nWeb developer at Seedrs.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE PAST:</h3>\r\nBefore joining Startup Scholarship Bruno built "explica.me", a website to easily find tutors near you. He is really fascinated by the internet and has been programming for the Web for about 4 years now.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE FUTURE:</h3>\r\nDuring the Startup Scholarship program and his internship Bruno expects to learn more about software development, agile processes and new business practices. In one year from now he hopes to be working in a startup and probably creating his own thing in his spare time.\r\n<h3>CREATIVITY INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n<div>Tesco, an online grocery store, installed posters on the South Korean subway with pictures of products and QR codes so people can scan that code, add that product to the cart on their smartphone and buy groceries while they wait.</div>\r\n<div>In less then 6 months their sales rose by 130%.</div>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">WOULD INVEST 1 MILLION $ IN:</h3>\r\n"It would probably be a web development startup to build products for other startups, empowering this way everyone to build their own MVPs. Something along the lines of 37signals".\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">FAVORITE PLACE ON EARTH:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Home.</p>', 'Startup Scholar: Bruno', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'startup-scholar-bruno', '', '', '2013-08-09 20:15:28', '2013-08-09 20:15:28', '', 0, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/?p=343', 0, 'post', '', 0),
