(348, 1, '2013-08-01 14:40:37', '2013-08-01 14:40:37', '<h3><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/SamuelCoelho.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-310" alt="SamuelCoelho" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/SamuelCoelho.png" /></a> <a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/TableAndFriends_a.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-124" alt="TableAndFriends_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/TableAndFriends_a.png" /></a></h3>\r\n<h3>Samuel "On Top of the World" Coelho</h3>\r\n22. Moita, Portugal.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">INTERNSHIP:</h3>\r\nGrowth Hacking (Integrating a tracking system to interact with multiple analytics providers like MixPanel, Google Analytics, Intercom, etc) at Table &amp; Friends.\r\n<h3>IN THE PAST:</h3>\r\nFinished his degree in Computer engineering and taught old people how to use a computer. In the past he thought that he wants to have a job in a big company to earn as much money as he can.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE FUTURE:</h3>\r\nAfter the Startup Scholarship program, Samuel expects to get knowledge about a lot of stuff (technical or non technical, the entrepreneurship world, etc). He would like to make a master degree to learn more. Luckily, he changed his mind about working for the big company. It sounds boring!\r\n<h3>CREATIVITY INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">"A company that''s names like a fruit... You know what I''m talking about... Apple! The name is not related to any piece of technology but you can''t forget it!"</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">WOULD INVEST 1 MILLION $ IN:</h3>\r\n"Something like a game for children and young students, enabling learning "hard stuff" in a fun and easy way. So, maybe more people would enjoy learn difficult things and we would get more engineers and scientists (The world needs them) ;)"\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">FAVORITE PLACE ON EARTH:</h3>\r\nWherever are the things that he likes.', 'Startup Scholar: Samuel', '', 