(353, 1, '2013-08-07 20:59:12', '2013-08-07 20:59:12', '<h3><a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/UmamiBox_a.png"><img class=" wp-image-125 alignleft" alt="UmamiBox_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/UmamiBox_a.png" width="137" height="137" /></a>UmamiBox</h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">EST: JULY 2012</h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">INDUSTRY: FOOD E-RETAIL</h3>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">WHAT?</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">UmamiBox brings original and different Portuguese flavors to your home.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">HOW?</h3>\r\nThe concept bases on bundling traditional food produced by the local farmers and manufacturers into the "UmamiBox". The box always contains something new and surprising and is shipped to customers for free. The idea perfectly fits into the fair trade thought.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">THE ORIGIN OF THE IDEA:</h3>\r\n"UmamiBox was born thanks to a group of friends passionate about food and who aspire to play an important role in disseminating small producers. Because we love discovering new things we thought of creating something that could reveal the most secret delights to everyone."', 'Startup: UmamiBox', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'startup-umamibox', '', '', '2013-08-07 20:59:12', '2013-08-07 20:59:12', '', 0, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/?p=353', 0, 'post', '', 0),
