(430, 1, '2013-09-04 14:27:41', '2013-09-04 14:27:41', '<a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/João_Vasques1.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-407" alt="João_Vasques1" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/João_Vasques1.png" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nJoão is an entrepreneur (a rebel and crazy one) that likes to build amazing stuff. He started building some Lego structures when he was a kid and today he crafts software to help people. Perfectionist, creative and curious, he has a constant hunger to learn more about everything he does not understand.\r\n\r\nThat hunger lead him to join Instituto Superior Técnico, where he received his Master’s Degree in Communication Networks Engineering in 2012.\r\n\r\nMartial arts aficionado, he’s a Taekwondo black belt where he jumps, kicks, fights and breaks some boards. In 2012, he represented Portugal in Taekwondo World Championship and placed 2nd.\r\n\r\nThe thing he enjoys the most is meet amazing people.\r\n\r\nIn The Startup Scholarship he gave a workshop on Git, Github and MongoDB.\r\n\r\nYou can follow him on Twitter at <a href="https://twitter.com/JoaoVasques" target="_blank">@JoaoVasques</a>.', 'Thank You Post: João Vasques', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'thank-you-post-joao-vasques', '', '', '2013-09-04 14:29:25', '2013-09-04 14:29:25', '', 0, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/?p=430', 0, 'post', '', 0),
