(440, 1, '2013-09-04 14:23:22', '2013-09-04 14:23:22', '<a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Daniel_Gomes1.png"><img class="size-full wp-image-406 alignleft" alt="Daniel_Gomes1" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Daniel_Gomes1.png" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nDaniel Gomes works as a Senior Software Engineer and PHP Expert at GuestCentric Systems in Lisbon, Portugal. He<b> </b>is an Open Source evangelist and contributor and an agile methodologies practitioner. He is the co-founder and co-organizer of <a href="http://phplx.net/" target="_blank">phplx</a>, a local php user group in Lisbon. He frequently speaks at local user groups and conferences.\r\n\r\nHe gave to our scholars a workshop on Git, Github, Vagrant and Puppet.\r\n\r\nYou can follow his blog at <a href="http://danielcsgomes.com/" target="_blank">danielcsgomes.com</a> or on Twitter at <a href="http://twitter.com/danielcsgomes" target="_blank">@danielcsgomes</a>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>phplx</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">phplx is a from the community to the community organization which organizes monthly technical meetups in Lisbon. Their goal is to connect the PHP community in Lisbon allowing people to come and share their knowledge and experiences as well as learning about new trends, tools or practises.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">Since November 2012, phplx has brought together like minded individuals to talk about php and related technologies.</p>', 'Thank You Post: Daniel Gomes', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '418-revision-11', '', '', '2013-09-04 14:23:22', '2013-09-04 14:23:22', '', 418, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/418-revision-11/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(441, 1, '2013-09-03 16:24:57', '2013-09-03 16:24:57', '<a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Michal.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-399" alt="Michal" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Michal.png" /></a> <a href="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Whistle_a1.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-127" alt="Whistle_a" src="http://startupscholarship.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/Whistle_a1.png" /></a>\r\n<h3>Michal "Ain''t No Mountain High Enough" Malcek</h3>\r\n26. Rimavska Sobota, Slovakia.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">INTERNSHIP:</h3>\r\nBusiness intern at Whistle. Doing initial marketing strategy, story and creating basic press releases from the marketing point of view.\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE PAST:</h3>\r\nMichal studied CEMS in Prague and Budapest. He did two internships at Google, in Prague and Dublin. He is also the co-founder of a local online retailer selling branded clothes in his town (<a href="http://www.activestyle.sk">www.activestyle.sk</a>).\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">IN THE FUTURE:</h3>\r\nCurrently Michal will try to start a simple, local freelancer-like platform focused only on marketing tasks. He would like to use his experience and contacts gained during The Startup Scholarship program and share them on local startup events, present the Lisbon startup experience, teach his local guys about lean startup methodology and growth hacking. He wants to stay in Slovakia for now and start his business. Hopefully in the future he will gain more international startup experience.\r\n<h3>CREATIVITY INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n<div>"By doing a creative direct marketing campaign for Google AdWords with a new, much better targeted approach (reaching the right segment with the right, suitable example) we reached extraordinary level of efficiency that was not seen before in such channel."</div>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr">WOULD INVEST 1 MILLION $ IN:</h3>\r\n"I would target one of the biggest problems of young people in Europe and USA - unemployment &amp; unemployability. I would build a platform connecting as many universities, students and companies as possible, to help companies get done stuff cheaper and review a student before hiring. For students it would give relevant practical experience with little effort to find an opportunity."\r\n<h3>FAVORITE PLACE ON EARTH:</h3>\r\n<p dir="ltr">His grandpa''s house, because it is so calm and close to the nature.</p>', 'Startup Scholar: Michal', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '398-revision-6', '', '', '2013-09-03 16:24:57', '2013-09-03 16:24:57', '', 398, 'http://startupscholarship.org/blog/398-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
